text: Brittany Hrynko (born April 24, 1993) is an American basketball player, currently a free agent. She was drafted by the Connecticut Sun of the Women's National Basketball Association in the 2015 WNBA Draft. She was then traded to the Atlanta Dream, but was released and later signed short-term contracts with the San Antonio Stars and Tulsa Shock. ==College== In Hrynko's final season at DePaul she averaged 19.1 points per game.
